source: src/support_status.rs
---
Node.js 18.x has reached end-of-life as of April 30, 2025 and is no longer supported. EOL versions no longer receive security updates or bug fixes from the Node.js project.

Supported versions: 20.x (LTS), 22.x (LTS), 24.x (LTS), 25.x (Current)

https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/nodejs-support#supported-node-js-versions
